Cordoval OS is a desktop-style software environment built using web technologies. It provides a controlled workspace for accessing first-party KDS applications and approved web-based services through embedded web views.

You acknowledge that:

Cordoval OS runs on top of an existing operating system

Applications may be delivered as web services

Features and behaviour may evolve over time

